data.title: 2007) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Register-Mail, The (Galesburg, IL) - Monday, May 21, 2007  Mary Jo Van Fleet  1944-2007  GALESBURG - Mary Jo Van Fleet, 62, 1145 Frank St., died at 8:25 a.m. Saturday (May 19, 2007) in Galesburg Cottage Hospital.  She was born Aug. 23, 1944, in Galesburg, the daughter of William D. and Eula Mae Downey Van Fleet. ...
